<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-11 13:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3993 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a BC-FLA-WATER-SHORTAGE-AR     03-11 1010
