<P>
   COXNET FOCUS 0312: CENSUS _ Check the mailbox, there's a form in
your future and it could change your life. Every 10 years, the
government conducts a head count of America. It may sound like a
dull exercise, but the results help determine how your are
represented in Congress and the state legislature and how federal
and state money is distributed to your city and school district.
(Holmes, Cox Washington Bureau).
