<P>
   TECH-VISAS _ WASHINGTON _ High-tech companies are running out of
time in this election-shortened congressional year to achieve one
of their prime goals _ expanding the H-1B visa program that brings
tens of thousands of skilled workers to American jobs. The
legislative maneuvering comes amid claims that the program is
harmful to American workers and even some immigrants. (Geewax, Cox
News Service).
</P>
