largest art museum in the USA, is also available.
</P>
<P>
   THEATER-PROFILE _ ATLANTA _ Profile of Sean Daniels, director of
Dad's Garage Theatre and self-appointed court jester of the Atlanta
theater scene, as he prepares a typically mad production: ``Action
Movie: The Play.'' (Hulbert, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 57.
WITH PHOTOS and LAYOUT. MOVED
</P>
<P>
   JAZZ-LACY _ An expatriate New Yorker who has lived in Paris for
most of the last 30 years, Steve Lacy has cultivated the brilliant
career most artists only fantasize about. (Dollar, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30. MOVED
